{"tid":1508853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 有關計算催淚彈數量","createTime":"2019-08-26T15:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T00:30:16.000Z","uid":237260,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"99fb50f80b4c97278857e11f18b7956a8f203045","tid":1508853,"uid":237260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"睇返PoPo公布 825荃葵青遊行, 發射催淚彈數量為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">145發</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69279693_2404099929675613_1991099499296063488_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQn9Rx7KR4MSdPOJOQnxiNnBGQelQ048J1SI6P64T9jdHUA_uVZ1n-rLzXMbD1slSE8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=ffc50874c60fc1f0b05eba72b669b36d&amp;oe=5DDB1586\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69279693_2404099929675613_1991099499296063488_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQn9Rx7KR4MSdPOJOQnxiNnBGQelQ048J1SI6P64T9jdHUA_uVZ1n-rLzXMbD1slSE8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dffc50874c60fc1f0b05eba72b669b36d%26oe%3D5DDB1586&h=ab573a26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好以為<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1發</span></span></strong>係咁， 屌你呢度已經係有<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5發</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/07/30/99/6626689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2F99%2F6626689.jpg&h=c5aa91bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇返呢張 825收集到<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">部分</span></span></strong>既大彈殼數量, 已經足足 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">46顆</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">46 x 5 = 230 &ne; 145， 計出黎就得知PoPo已經比左假數</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69122382_1292517677577764_5345231969766604800_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQk5lkSUR7GAO-DVBRxJG-zcILXu-mKs78akZUhNQHxi7B6H8Y5eYjrIO3uS8kw4mJY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=4b6f678513660e01068f3f38aa76e6a5&amp;oe=5E0D6CA1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69122382_1292517677577764_5345231969766604800_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQk5lkSUR7GAO-DVBRxJG-zcILXu-mKs78akZUhNQHxi7B6H8Y5eYjrIO3uS8kw4mJY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D4b6f678513660e01068f3f38aa76e6a5%26oe%3D5E0D6CA1&h=b43aa103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果當PoPo條數係真又會點呢?<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>145 x 5 = 725</strong></span></span>, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">琴日足足射左700發啊！！！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">結論一係PoPo報細數, 一係PoPo一直誤導緊個計算方法</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩大家記住以後分清楚</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一顆有5發</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一顆有5發</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一顆有5發</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一顆有5發</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一顆有5發</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一顆有5發</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6db89f5812084b88a939daf6457835c992dfa66e","tid":1508853,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"